values: Last night I went to my Drama Departments annual Spotlight Awards. It was my first time going so I did not know what to expect. The theme was Las Vegas. I was a Trophy Monkey, the person who hands out the trophies. That was fun. Everyone said that I was the best dressed. It was sort of shocking because I decided what outfit to wear at the last minute. And the best part of all was that I won an award. I was totally not expecting it at all. My drama teacher picked me a the overall actor in my drama class. I am so happy, and then I am so tired. I stayed up really late last night and now I have a killer headache. I just want to go back to sleep. ZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZ.

I just got back from the orthodontist. They hurt me so much. They get paid to cause ppl pain. The good thing is that I get my braces off in about 4 weeks.  I can't wait....well yes I can, considering I have been waiting 5 years to get them off.  Very, Very long story and I don not want to get into it. 

My mom was being such a butt today. She would not let me go over to my friend's house.....TO DO HOMEWORK!!!!!!!!!!!!  And honest to gosh it was to do homeword.  Seriously, she expects me to keep straight A's without any help at all. Is that possible?  I mean even smart ppl need help once in a while.  And if I do not get straight A's then I won't be able to do any more plays.  My parents are really strict.  Just because they did not make the grade does not mean that we have to be punishe for it. Well, I am going to take my anger out on something else now.! Bye.

I am in the after play blues. I just finished the play Little Shop of Horros. I played Ronette the Doo Wop girl. For any of you who don't know, she is the lead doo wop girl. It was a really amazing part. And now I am really sad that it is over. I really wish it would have gone on longer.  I really miss all of my friends. Anyone reading this like LSOH? Write me. I really need to talk about it. Maybe it will make me more cheerful!

hey, this is my first entry in my new journal. I am really really hyper right now. My friend just showed my how to do this because I was bored and here I am. I really do not know what to talk about. I am excited because I get out of school in 9 days. I can't wait until summer. I get to go on a cruise and then to Las Vegas. Well I am going to go now. Bye!
